{"id": 3385, "title": "Ticket #3385: Add BOINC as a grid universe-supported service", "description": "<blockquote>\nWe want to support BOINC as a service that Condor can submit jobs to. This would appear as a new service type under the grid universe.\n\n<p>See <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1BvrCXw9Oks8MBketFoYjl0Ck2YBGScYGKVwhYrrdhwY/edit\">design document</a> for details.\n\n</p><p><span class=\"subsection\"></span></p><h3>Milestones </h3>\n\n<p></p><ul>\n<li>Outline interaction between HTCondor and BOINC <strong>(DONE)</strong>\n</li><li>[2 days effort] Complete details of BOINC GAHP protocol <strong>(DONE)</strong>\n</li><li>[? days effort] Implement BOINC GAHP <strong>(DONE)</strong>\n</li><li>[7 days effort] Add BOINC code to gridmanager  <strong>(DONE)</strong>\n</li><li>Add BOINC code as an external (Jaime Frey)\n</li><li>[5 days effort] Integration testing (Jaime Frey and Dave Anderson)\n</li><li>[3 days effort] Write automated regression tests (Jaime Frey)</li></ul>\n</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3540\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3540'); return false;\" title=\"Add grid-type boinc to gridmanager\">#3540</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nAdd grid-type boinc to gridmanager</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2014-May-21 16:07</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck